PIXON TECHNOLOGI said unconsolidated sales
in May fell 27.90% to NT$72,673,000 from NT$100,798,000,
according to a statement filed to the  Taiwan Stock Exchange .  (Figures are in thousands of New Taiwan dollars)  =================================================================  5/2012           5/2011
Sales             72,673          100,798    
YOY%             -27.90%   -----------------Year-to-date-----------------
Sales            410,460          463,695    
YOY%             -11.48% 
=================================================================
 